Subject: [Bioc-devel] new DBI and RSQLite versions
Message-ID: <DM5PR12MB1578541B402FB94FA79027C0FFD80@DM5PR12MB1578.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>

Hi,

Last week new versions of DBI and RSQLite were released on CRAN:

  https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/DBI/news.html

  https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/RSQLite/news.html

Highlights include

- dbGetQuery is now exported from DBI, not RSQLite

- deGetPreparedQuery has been deprecated and replaced by dbGetQuery

The following packages have a problem with either the deprecated
dbGetPreparedQuery or improperly imported dbGetQuery. Please see the
build report for specific errors and commit a fix to both release and
devel branches.

attract
categoryCompare
CNEr
crlmm
cummeRbund
DASC
fastLiquidAssociation
GGtools
IsoformSwitchAnalyzeR
MatrixRider
spliceR
TFBSTools

Thanks.
Valerie


